{"text_id":239705,"tokens":["Starting"," in"," the"," late"," ","1","9","5","0","s",","," American"," computer"," scientist"," Paul"," Baran"," developed"," the"," concept"," Distributed"," Adaptive"," Message"," Block"," Switching"," with"," the"," goal"," to"," provide"," a"," fault","-","tolerant",","," efficient"," routing"," method"," for"," tele","communication"," between"," geographically"," dispersed"," points","."," The"," paper"," describes"," a"," \"","virtual","\""," router"," that"," automatically"," directs"," data"," flows"," as"," needed"," throughout"," an"," entire"," distributed"," system"," to"," adapt"," and"," maintain"," connectivity"," among"," networked"," devices"," at"," any"," given"," time"," under"," changing"," conditions","."," It"," is"," especially"," useful"," where"," high"," reliability"," over"," long"," distances"," is"," required","."," The"," messages"," are"," directed"," from"," one"," switch"," node"," or"," edge"," device",","," usually"," referred"," to"," as"," the"," source"," start"," point"," (","SSP",")"," and"," destination"," end"," point"," (","DEP","),"," to"," another"," SSP","DEP"," pair"," through"," a"," path"," tree","."," Each"," route"," on"," this"," tree"," must"," be"," capable"," of"," handling"," multiple"," data"," flow"," paths"," simultaneously","."," A"," typical"," message"," may"," have"," many"," different"," possible"," routes",","," each"," assigned"," to"," specific"," intermediate"," nodes"," along"," its"," path",","," called"," hop"," count"," values","."," If"," there"," ever"," was"," more"," than"," one"," route"," available"," to"," a"," node",","," then"," it"," would"," use"," the"," shortest"," path"," first"," and"," only"," change"," routes"," if"," the"," new"," path"," took"," longer"," than"," the"," old"," one","."," In"," spite"," of"," this"," simplicity",","," the"," processor"," overhead"," incurred"," by"," determining"," all"," possible"," routes"," can"," become"," prohib","itively"," large","."," By"," using"," a"," dynamic"," routing"," algorithm",","," the"," number"," of"," possible"," routes"," identified"," per"," second"," decreases"," exponentially"," in"," proportion"," to"," the"," size"," of"," the"," input"," data"," stream",";"," thus"," allowing"," for"," massive"," parallelism"," at"," low"," CPU"," usage"," costs","."," This"," advanced"," application"," of"," distributed"," computing"," is"," now"," known"," as"," Baran","'","s"," Adaptive"," Routing"," Algorithm"," (","BARA",")."],"sub_source":"squad","model":"opt_6.7b","label":1}